0.1.name: wordpress/fun-with-photo-data
0.1.description:
WordPress 2.5 now extracts and saves the EXIF and IPTC data that is stored in photographs.

WordPress 2.5 also introduces shortcodes, a shorthand way of including data in posts.

This plugin makes use of these shortcodes to display the photo data as part of your post.
